      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/companies-bolster-currency-hedges-after-trump-win-tariffs-loom-2024-11-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[跨国公司正在加强外汇对冲策略，以保护其海外收益免受唐纳德·特朗普再次担任总统可能带来的更大汇率波动的影响。]]></description>
